@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.16
    v2 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.66 / tmp + 0.67)) - wp.sin(tmp))
    tmp = wp.sin((0.42 / tmp))
    v0 = v2
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.abs(v2 + 0.14) - wp.cos(v2 + 0.14)))
    v2 = v0
    v0 = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.98 + v0 + 0.90) + wp.exp(v0 + 0.04)))
    data[tid] = v0
